1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What if you could remember more just by creating it yourself?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,400
This is the generation effect, a powerful concept in psychology.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:12,800
When you generate info—like writing or drawing—your brain retains it better.

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:17,600
Studies show this effect is stronger than just reading or passively learning.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:22,400
So next time you need to remember something, try creating it yourself!

6
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:24,400
Curious about more mind hacks?

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,400
Like and follow for more!
